title: Chaco Canyon Organic Cafe - West Seattle
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, International, Organic, Juice bar, Take-out
description: The second Chaco Canyon organic cafe location. Offers sandwiches, rice and quinoa bowls, salads, soups, raw food cuisine, baked treats, organic coffee, juices, and smoothies. This location has a kids menu as well. Sunday brunch is served from 9am-3pm. Everything vegan, except for cow's milk.
